    "combat3": {
      "name": "The Bell Tolls! The Hunt Is On!",
      "description": "Prune gently swings the Witchlure Bell, dealing Anemo DMG to nearby opponents. After this, the Bell will enter the Hunter-Seeker mode.\n\nWitchlure Bell: Hunter-Seeker\nIn this mode, the Witchlure Bell will follow the current active character, attacking surrounding opponents at intervals and dealing AoE Anemo DMG. This DMG is considered Elemental Burst DMG.",
      "descriptionRaw": "Prune gently swings the Witchlure Bell, dealing <color=#80FFD7FF>Anemo DMG</color> to nearby opponents. After this, the Bell will enter the Hunter-Seeker mode.\n\n<color=#FFD780FF>Witchlure Bell: Hunter-Seeker</color>\nIn this mode, the Witchlure Bell will follow the current active character, attacking surrounding opponents at intervals and dealing <color=#80FFD7FF>AoE Anemo DMG</color>. This DMG is considered Elemental Burst DMG.",
